description:
## Files
- __manifest__.py (modify)
- static/src/components/blueprint_widget/blueprint_widget.js (create)
- static/src/components/blueprint_widget/blueprint_widget.xml (create)
- static/src/components/blueprint_widget/blueprint_widget.scss (create)

## What to do

### 1. Modify __manifest__.py
Add an assets key to the dict. Place it AFTER the existing "data" key and BEFORE "installable". Add:

    'assets': {
        'web.assets_backend': [
            'pest_control/static/src/components/blueprint_widget/blueprint_widget.js',
            'pest_control/static/src/components/blueprint_widget/blueprint_widget.xml',
            'pest_control/static/src/components/blueprint_widget/blueprint_widget.scss',
        ],
    },

Do NOT modify any other key in the manifest.

### 2. Create blueprint_widget.js
Create file at static/src/components/blueprint_widget/blueprint_widget.js with content:

/** @odoo-module **/
import { registry } from "@web/core/registry";
import { Component, useState, useRef, onMounted } from "@odoo/owl";

export class BlueprintWidget extends Component {
    static template = "pest_control.BlueprintWidget";
    static props = {
        value: { optional: true },
        record: { optional: true },
        readonly: { type: Boolean, optional: true },
    };

    setup() {
        this.state = useState({
            traps: [],
            mode: "view",
            loading: true,
        });
    }
}

registry.category("fields").add("blueprint_canvas", BlueprintWidget);

### 3. Create blueprint_widget.xml
Create file at static/src/components/blueprint_widget/blueprint_widget.xml:

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<templates xml:space="preserve">
    <t t-name="pest_control.BlueprintWidget">
        <div class="blueprint-widget-container">
            <t t-if="state.loading">
                <div class="blueprint-loading">Cargando plano...</div>
            </t>
            <t t-else="">
                <div class="blueprint-canvas-wrapper" style="position: relative;">
                    <span>Widget de plano interactivo - en desarrollo</span>
                </div>
            </t>
        </div>
    </t>
</templates>

### 4. Create blueprint_widget.scss
Create file at static/src/components/blueprint_widget/blueprint_widget.scss:

.blueprint-widget-container {
    width: 100%;
    min-height: 400px;
    background: #f5f5f5;
    border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
    border-radius: 4px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
}

.blueprint-canvas-wrapper {
    width: 100%;
    position: relative;
}

.blueprint-loading {
    color: #6c757d;
    font-style: italic;
}

## Dont
- Do not modify any existing keys in __manifest__.py besides adding assets
- Do not change the data list or depends list
- Create directories as needed (static/src/components/blueprint_widget/)
